query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS binary_tree_positions (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  distributorId INT NOT NULL,
  parentId INT,
  sponsorId INT NOT NULL,
  position ENUM('left','right') NOT NULL,
  depthLevel INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX idx_distributorId (distributorId),
  INDEX idx_parentId (parentId),
  INDEX idx_sponsorId (sponsorId),
  UNIQUE KEY unique_distributorId (distributorId)
)
